{"tid":1191600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung 擬關閉東莞廠房 越南將成手機生產基地","createTime":"2019-06-08T04:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T06:13:28.000Z","uid":39464,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"11a7ca79b7c1d0a28cf74634e289d1fbec9c254a","tid":1191600,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:13:07.000Z","msg":"越來越多手機品牌選擇撤離中國大陸，在東南亞和印度設置廠房，早前 Sony 關閉北京廠房後遷移到泰國生產手機，而多間台灣代工商則將部份生產線改設在印度，LG 亦已經將手機生產工廠轉到越南。最新消息指 Samsung 亦會將大陸最後一根手機廠房關閉，然後改在越南生產。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/03-6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F03-6.png&h=5aace143&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSamsung 去年 4 月和 12 月，分別關閉了深圳和天津的手機生產線，改為在越南北寧和太原設置生產線組裝手機，據說現時有一半 Samsung 手機都在越南生產。由於 Samsung 手機在大陸面對激烈競爭，加上中國人力成本上漲，有指 Samsung 在評估後認為不再適合在大陸生產手機，決定將 1992 年開始營運，在 2006 年起生產手機的惠州廠房於 9 月關閉。<br />\n<br />\n惠州廠房在 2017 年聘請了超過 6,000 員工，年產量高達 6,300 萬部；消息指 Samsung 會以自願離職方式遣散員工，在本月中前簽字離職的會有賠償。Samsung 高層對傳聞未有承認和否認，只表示正調整惠州廠房的產量以應對大陸的嚴峻環境和劇烈競爭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/08/samsung-may-close-dongguan-factory-this-sept/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F08%2Fsamsung-may-close-dongguan-factory-this-sept%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW8z%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=563e4d6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/08/samsung-may-close-dongguan-factory-this-sept/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"d4be569f02c311b06d0be381760943651cb7867d","tid":1191600,"uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:19:45.000Z","msg":"人類遲早唔用手提電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中国又贏"},{"pid":"d86709f173cde8e307439fde9fa3f73d356